The
.B openwatch
fleet control plane consumes kensa-go's
.B api/
contract for orchestration. See
.UR https://github.com/Hanalyx/openwatch
.UE .
.PP
The rule corpus ships separately as the
.B kensa-rules
package. Source:
.UR https://github.com/Hanalyx/kensa
.UE .
