.PP
Known issues:
.IP \(bu 2
.B noopSigner
placeholder: evidence envelopes in v1.0 carry empty signature bytes.
The Ed25519 signer ships in v1.1 (Track L Phase 1 / M7 task #12).
.IP \(bu 2
The
.B agent
subcommand is a v1.0 placeholder; the actual multi-call agent binary
lands in v1.1 with the kernel-primitive migration (Track L Phase 1).
.IP \(bu 2
The
.B coverage
subcommand is a deprecated alias for
.B mechanisms
in v1.0; in v1.1 it will be repurposed for framework control coverage
reporting. Migrate scripts before upgrading.
